com.orchestranetworks.service
Interface ReadOnlyProcedure

All Superinterfaces:
Procedure
public interface ReadOnlyProcedure
extends Procedure

Interface to be implemented for read-only transactions.

A class implementing the Procedure interface can additionally implement the ReadOnlyProcedure interface, to manifest that this procedure will not modify any data in the EBX5 repository. This allows other read-only transactions in the same data space to be run fully concurrently.

If a class implementing this interface however modifies EBX5 data in its execute method, an UnsupportedOperationException will be thrown.
